## Deferred to v0.5.0 (Not Today)

These items are **intentionally excluded** from v0.4.27 because they require design, testing, or infrastructure:

| Task | Why Deferred |
|------|-------------|
| Fresh checkout test setup | Requires packaging strategy decision (Poetry vs pip) |
| Packaging boundaries (PYTHONPATH cleanup) | Requires monorepo package strategy decision |
| DB/Redis backing for mock state | Requires Redis schema design, migration testing, multi-instance coordination |
| Systemd hardening | Requires testing on actual systemd systems; can't verify in dev container |
| Observability (/metrics, Prometheus) | Requires deploying monitoring stack; not a code-only change |
| Load tests | Requires load testing infrastructure; not a quick fix |
| Secret rotation policy | Requires Vault/Secrets Manager deployment; ops task |
| Smart contract mainnet | v1.0.0 only |
| External security audit | v1.0.0 only |

